{"tid":1563674,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"連吃5年生蛇膽　大陸仔腦部遭寄生蟲鑽入啃食","createTime":"2019-09-12T13:14:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T15:14:34.000Z","uid":122,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"58cdab482b7ce39f1d2980f37a3141a11e3fa548","tid":1563674,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T13:14:56.000Z","msg":"中國一名28歲男子，從16年前開始出現癲癇、頭暈症狀，就診後發現，他分腦組織已經被寄生蟲吃掉，詢問之下，才知道他被寄生蟲感染的原因，是吃了5年生蛇膽。<br />\n<br />\n據《澎湃新聞》報導，近日，中國浙江一名男子到醫院就診，稱癲癇持續16年，醫生詢問後得知，男子父親是當地知名獵戶常年捕蛇，為了讓孩子強身健體，專門抓蛇取出蛇膽給兒子生吃。男子告訴醫生，父親從他7歲開始，就餵他生蛇膽，吃了5年。 醫生聽聞後判斷男子的癲癇可能是寄生蟲感染，檢測後確認，男子是曼氏裂頭蚴感染，進入腦部後吸取腦細胞營養發育長大，且大腦會被不可修復地破壞。<br />\n<br />\n9月10日，醫生指蟲體寄生部位，位於男子的腦功能區，手術可能造成部分腦功能喪失，只好選擇了口服驅蟲藥物治療，「小夥現已好轉出院，多次隨訪未再發作癲癇。」"},{"pid":"a5a46b85821a1894016e912cb6582e2083842936","tid":1563674,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T13:15:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"73217541ee28fb197d1c1047af080eb0f2ecff37","tid":1563674,"uid":78873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T13:16:53.000Z","msg":"生食 仲要係大陸蛇<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6665d057c6e485d8d7686ba644ef7aac8a7057e5","tid":1563674,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci